Package models

Class User

java.lang.Object
models.User
public class User extends Object
User class representing a user in the contact management system. Demonstrates encapsulation by keeping fields private and providing controlled access through getters and setters. This is an entity class that maps to the users table in the database.
Version:
1.0
Author:
CMPE-343 Project Group
